### New Product Prompt Tab

#### [NEW] [product_tab.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/product_tab.py)

Self-contained UI + logic for generating product photography prompts:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  📸 Product Prompt Generator                             │
├───────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ LEFT PANEL    │ RIGHT PANEL: Results                     │
│               │                                          │
│ Object:       │ ┌──────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ [iPhone 16  ] │ │ 1. A dramatic low-angle hero shot... │ │
│               │ │ 2. Top-down flatlay composition...   │ │
│ Style: [▼]    │ │ 3. Extreme close-up macro shot of... │ │
│ Tier:  [▼]    │ │ 4. Lifestyle in-situ photograph...   │ │
│ Count: [8]    │ │ 5. Side profile silhouette shot...   │ │
│               │ │ ...                                   │ │
│ [▶ Generate]  │ └──────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│ [💾 Save]     │                                          │
│ [📋 Copy All] │                                          │
└───────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Fields:**
| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| Object Name | Text input | Product name (e.g. "iPhone 16 Pro Max", "Nike Air Jordan 1") |
| Style | ComboBox | Reuses existing styles from [styles/](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/ui/projects_section.py#171-175) folder |
| Tier | ComboBox | Flash / Pro |
| Prompt Count | Entry | Number of prompts to generate (default: 8) |

**System Prompt Strategy**: The style file becomes the system prompt. A specialized user message instructs the model to generate N unique product photography prompts with varied angles/compositions:

```
Generate {count} unique, detailed image generation prompts for product photography of: "{object_name}"

Each prompt must showcase the product from a DIFFERENT perspective:
- Various camera angles (hero shot, top-down, 45°, low angle, eye-level, macro)
- Different compositions (isolated, lifestyle, in-context, flatlay, floating)
- Varied lighting (studio, natural, dramatic, rim light, soft diffused)
- Multiple focal points (full product, detail/texture, branding, specific feature)

Format: Return ONLY the prompts, numbered 1 to {count}, one per line.
Each prompt should be self-contained and ready for image generation.
```

**Actions:**
- **Generate**: Sends a single API request → model returns N prompts in one response
- **Save**: Saves results to `output_dir/{object_name}_product_prompts.txt`
- **Copy All**: Copies all prompts to clipboard

